  "text": "• Ycut SAW resonators are expected to have the resonance frequencies of 87.2 MHz and 99.9 MHz, with corresponding SAW velocities of 3488 m/s and 3997 m/s, respectively [CITATION_1] . The samples are fixed with varnish on a sample holder and the IDT ports are wire-bonded to SMA connectors as shown in FIG. 1 ",
